Enum Class NonTermUnit

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<NonTermUnit>
LexicalAnalyzer.NonTermUnit
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<NonTermUnit>, Constable
public enum NonTermUnit extends Enum<NonTermUnit>
Enumeration of non-terminal symbols used in the grammar. Each constant corresponds to a production rule in the parser.
